Silgranit sink by BLANCO and faucet with a pull-out spray of the same brand and shade. The living room with kitchen features a total of 7 lighting options, allowing you to choose the right setting according to your mood and type of activity (while cooking, you will definitely appreciate plenty of light, but preferences change when watching TV or having guests) and additionally comes with a practical single remote control for all. The rooms are equipped with radiators with thermostatic valves, and the bathroom features a towel radiator, all of which can be controlled centrally using a digital thermostat. The higher standard of Europalace offers very high-quality wood - aluminum windows, which not only provide thermal insulation but also effectively soundproof the apartment from the outside environment. The high quality, comfort, and safety of living are enhanced by nearby sports and relaxation facilities, as well as a variety of commercial and dining establishments in the area. The location also offers excellent access to the city center and to the expressway connections. The property is located in a highly sought-after area, offering complete civic amenities and many additional benefits. The Europalace complex itself offers premium services : the entire property is monitored 24 hours a day by a security service (SBS), with camera surveillance and monitoring of common areas, underground parking, and more. The building itself houses a restaurant, a dental clinic, a client center of the Ministry of Interior of the Slovak Republic, as well as the headquarters of our real estate agency MGM. It is just a few minutes' walk to grocery stores (Kaufland, LIDL), Dubeň shopping center, restaurants, primary and nursery schools, fitness facilities, ŽILPO polyclinic, and the University of Žilina. Tennis courts, an indoor swimming pool, a summer swimming pool, an athletic complex, and the Chrasť forest park sports and recreation zone are just a short distance away. The city center of Žilina is within a 5-minute drive, or a 15-minute walk.
